<li id="cite_note-StatsWarCost-148"><b><a href="#cite_ref-StatsWarCost_148-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFNofi2001">Nofi, Al (2001-06-13). <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070711050249/http://www.cwc.lsu.edu/other/stats/warcost.htm" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070711050249/http://www.cwc.lsu.edu/other/stats/warcost.htm" rel="nofollow">"Statistics on the War's Costs"</a>. Louisiana State University<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070711050249/http://www.cwc.lsu.edu/other/stats/warcost.htm" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070711050249/http://www.cwc.lsu.edu/other/stats/warcost.htm" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20070711050249/http://www.cwc.lsu.edu/other/stats/warcost.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-10-14</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Statistics+on+the+War%27s+Costs&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Nofi&amp;rft.aufirst=Al&amp;rft.au=Nofi%2C+Al&amp;rft.date=2001-06-13&amp;rft.pub=Louisiana+State+University&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070711050249%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.cwc.lsu.edu%2Fother%2Fstats%2Fwarcost.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:American_Civil_War"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
