<li id="cite_note-HarvardCraig-150"><b><a href="#cite_ref-HarvardCraig_150-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFLambert">Lambert, Craig (May-June 2001). <a href="http://www.harvardmagazine.com/on-line/050155.html" class="external text" title="http://www.harvardmagazine.com/on-line/050155.html" rel="nofollow">"The Deadliest War"</a>. Harvard Magazine<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.harvardmagazine.com/on-line/050155.html" class="external free" title="http://www.harvardmagazine.com/on-line/050155.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.harvardmagazine.com/on-line/050155.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-10-14</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Deadliest+War&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Lambert&amp;rft.aufirst=Craig&amp;rft.au=Lambert%2C+Craig&amp;rft.date=May-June+2001&amp;rft.pub=Harvard+Magazine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.harvardmagazine.com%2Fon-line%2F050155.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:American_Civil_War"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
