<td class="navbox-group" style=";padding-left:0em;padding-right:0em;width:9.0em; background:#c0c0c0;;">
<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;"><a href="/wiki/Origins_of_the_American_Civil_War" title="Origins of the American Civil War">Origins</a></div>
